data.text:
James Kennedy is portrayed by Daniel Durant. He was Love Quinn's late husband; they were married in July of 2016.

Biography[]

He developed cancer, which Love saw him through. It is originally believed that he died shortly after, but later it is revealed that he went into remission, and decided that he wanted to leav.

e Love. In an attempt to immobilize him and therefore put him in the position to need Love again and giving her the ability to convince him not to leave her- Love poisoned his food with aconite. Unaware of the ideal dosage, she accidentally gave him too much causing his death.

Appearances[]

Season 2 (1/10)[]

Farewell, My Bunny (flashback)

Trivia[]

James' actor, Daniel Durant is also deaf in real life.
